So, she had the operation of  HYPERLINK "http://www.baidu.com/link?url=QVPwitulcUUdUjL-QwKarF4tsq6QBpKA8F6jFONYzyGDnXE_v_XDoHS0Nb8oAXtsixCAe3_jnkz4FbPFACheI9VOUnbfxFf_jNXZtv5keJkcfvXZAAGO5KdRJxadzw_c" \t "_blank" aortic valve replacement.

