Go Seung Tak.

21:24.600 --> 21:27.930
Tell us about  HYPERLINK "http://www.baidu.com/link?url=QVPwitulcUUdUjL-QwKarF4tsq6QBpKA8F6jFONYzyGDnXE_v_XDoHS0Nb8oAXtsixCAe3_jnkz4FbPFACheI9VOUnbfxFf_jNXZtv5keJkcfvXZAAGO5KdRJxadzw_c" \t "_blank" the bicuspid aortic valve.

